yarn cypress:run --record

# Verify Electron binary builds correctly
yarn workspace @packages/electron build-binary
```

### Fix Failing Tests
```bash
# Run tests and fix any failures
yarn test

# Common issues:
# - Node.js API changes
# - Electron API changes
# - Chromium behavior changes
```

