## Common Issues and Solutions

### Integrity Check Failures
```bash
# Update fs.readFileSync string representation in:
# /scripts/binary/binary-integrity-check-source.js
# Create throwaway script: console.log(fs.readFileSync.toString())
# Run with: electron throwaway-script.js
```

### ResizeObserver Errors
```bash
# Update error message matching in support files
# Error message changes between Chromium versions
```

### Electron Crashes After Protocol Database Init
```bash
# Usually due to mismatched better-sqlite3 prebuild
# Solution: git clean -xfd && yarn
# Ensure latest OS version
```

### Node ABI Out of Date
```bash
# Error: "Could not detect abi for version X.X.X and runtime electron"
# Check for newer @electron/rebuild version
# Update node-abi resolution in package.json
```

## Files to Search and Update

### Global Search for Old Versions
```bash
# Search for old Node.js version across codebase
grep -r "OLD_NODE_VERSION" . --exclude-dir=node_modules --exclude-dir=dist

# Search for old Electron version
grep -r "OLD_ELECTRON_VERSION" . --exclude-dir=node_modules --exclude-dir=dist

# Update any found references
```

### Key Files Checklist
- [ ] `/package.json` - electron version, engines.node, node-abi resolution
- [ ] `/.node-version` - Node.js version
- [ ] `/.nvmrc` - Node.js version  
- [ ] `/docker-compose.yml` - base-internal image
- [ ] `/.circleci/workflows.yml` - base-internal images
- [ ] `/packages/server/package.json` - better-sqlite3 version
- [ ] `/packages/types/package.json` - better-sqlite3 version
- [ ] `/system-tests/test-binary/*` - Docker image references
- [ ] All `@types/node` references across monorepo

## External Dependencies (Manual Steps)

These require manual updates in external repositories:

### Docker Images
- Update `cypress-docker-images` repository
- Create new `base-internal` images with matching Node.js/Chromium versions
- Publish to Docker Hub

### Binary Publishing
- Update `cypress-publish-binary` repository
- Update electron version in package.json
- Update CircleCI configuration
- Update Docker image references

## Validation Commands

```bash
# Verify Electron version
yarn workspace @packages/electron getElectronVersion

# Verify Node.js version
yarn workspace @packages/electron getElectronNodeVersion

# Build and test
yarn build
yarn test

# Test binary
yarn binary-smoke-test
```

